_sText:
Hello!

This is my first "professional" map!

This map features a central, unfinished 2 story building, where the action takes places. The map has plenty of fun places to stab people from, you could sneak up behind them; use the building to flank them; drop out of nowhere; charge right in; or get them from around a corner, just try and experiment and stuff.

Check the screenshots for more info!
